Do the lines and let’s get out of here, for Christ's sake!

00:05:52.151 --> 00:05:55.083
That stuff you did for me
at the Apollo...

00:05:55.083 --> 00:05:57.218
[LAUGHTER]
...but it was funny.

00:05:57.431 --> 00:05:59.830
When Bob De Niro and I are
on the same stage together

00:05:59.830 --> 00:06:02.688
these days it’s usually to give
each other lifetime achievement awards.

00:06:02.688 --> 00:06:04.690
[LAUGHTER]
So we see each other mainly

00:06:04.690 --> 00:06:07.648
at award ceremonies and memorial
services...

00:06:07.648 --> 00:06:09.406
[LAUGHTER]

00:06:09.406 --> 00:06:12.918
...like tonight.
[LAUGHTER]

00:06:12.918 --> 00:06:15.153
Though, if I'd be directing this,
I don't think I would have gone

00:06:15.153 --> 00:06:18.896
for the open casket.
[LAUGHTER]

00:06:18.896 --> 00:06:22.653
Rest in peace, old friend.
[LAUGHTER]

00:06:22.653 --> 00:06:25.318
