00:06:28.294 --> 00:06:30.448
Jerry Seinfield, Dave Letterman.
Everybody was there.

00:06:30.448 --> 00:06:32.899
It was really pretty wild that night.
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:06:32.899 --> 00:06:35.824
No, you're a great guy, Don.
You are.

00:06:36.544 --> 00:06:37.672
Not that we give a shit.

00:06:37.672 --> 00:06:39.836
[LAUGHTER]

00:06:40.307 --> 00:06:42.233
We’ve always been talking
about comedians.

00:06:42.233 --> 00:06:45.210
We did, years ago, "King of Comedy,”
we did the comic...

00:06:45.210 --> 00:06:46.445
&gt;&gt; Yeah.
&gt;&gt; The whole idea of the stand-up,

00:06:46.445 --> 00:06:48.118
and what the stand-up
has to go through.

00:06:48.118 --> 00:06:50.224
&gt;&gt; Yeah.
&gt;&gt; In one, stand there. In one...

00:06:50.224 --> 00:06:52.354
&gt;&gt; Yeah.
