that had a ring of truth,

00:08:38.630 --> 00:08:40.906
yet a lot of affection to it.

00:08:40.906 --> 00:08:43.037
I want him to be around
for a long time.

00:08:43.037 --> 00:08:43.780
Yeah.

00:08:43.780 --> 00:08:46.076
They always joke going "Mr. Warmth,"
but he is.

00:08:46.076 --> 00:08:48.481
[LAUGHTER]

00:08:48.481 --> 00:08:50.581
It's good what you’re doing here,
because it's like an oral history

00:08:50.581 --> 00:08:55.224
